<p>This page explains all options for configuring the User Interface in Preferences in <app>Parabolic</app>.</p>

<terms>
    <item>
        <title>Theme</title>
        <p>The theme for the user interface.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Default: System</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Completed Notification Trigger</title>
        <p>The trigger used for showing completed download notifications when the application is not active.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Default: For each download</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Prevent Suspend</title>
        <p>If enabled, the system while be prevented from suspending while Parabolic is running.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Valor per defecte: desactivat</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Recuperar les desc√†rregues fallides</title>
        <p>If enabled, Parabolic will track the running and queued downloads and restart them if necessary if the application crashes and is restarted.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Valor per defecte: activat</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Baixa immediatament despr√©s de validar</title>
		<p>Bypasses the download options selection in the Add Download dialog and immediately downloads a validated media using previously selected options.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Valor per defecte: desactivat</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Download History Length</title>
        <p>The amount of time to keep download history saved.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Default: One Week</p>
        </note>
    </item>
</terms>
